There are a number of ways to communicate with the oVirt Community. [[#Mailing lists | Mailing lists]], [[#IRC | IRC]], our [http://bugzilla.redhat.com bug tracker] and [http://gerrit.ovirt.org our patch review system].

{{:Mailing lists}}

= IRC =

We are on '''irc.oftc.net''' server on '''#ovirt''' channel

== Weekly Meetings ==
oVirt has a weekly synchronization meeting which is held on IRC. Information can be seen on the [[Meetings]] page.

= Bug tracker and code review =

You can report bugs, or discuss possible solutions to issues, on [http://bugzilla.redhat.com the project bug tracker (ovirt project)].

We use Gerrit to review patches. To comment on a patch, or submit a patch for review, please read [[working with oVirt Gerrit]].

